==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: fizgig
<hw>fiz"gig`</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Fizz</ets> + <ets>gig</ets>
whirling thing.]</ety> <def>A firework, made of damp powder, which makes
a fizzing or hissing noise when it explodes.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>fizgig</ent>⟦br⟧

